graph TD
    TrendServer[Trending Service Node.js]
    Internet((Internet / APIs))
    TrackServer[Tracking Service]
    RedisTrackList[(Redis Tracking List)]
    RMQ{{RabbitMQ}}
    Analyzer[Python Analyzer]
    CoreServer[Core Server Node.js]
    RedisCache[(Redis Cache)]

    subgraph Discovery
        TrendServer -->|1. Scan APIs for Volume Spikes| Internet
        TrendServer -->|2. Spot Breakout Ticker 'GME'| TrendServer
        TrendServer -->|3. HTTP Track 'GME' High Priority 48hr TTL| TrackServer
    end
    
    subgraph Execution
        TrackServer -->|4. Save Temporary Job| RedisTrackList
        TrackServer -->|5. Scrape Hourly| Internet
        TrackServer -->|6. Publish High-Priority Task| RMQ
    end
    
    subgraph Processing & Cache
        RMQ -->|7. Process Immediately| Analyzer
        Analyzer -->|8. Publish Results| RMQ
        RMQ -->|9. Deliver Results| CoreServer
        CoreServer -->|10. Overwrite Live Score w/ Short TTL| RedisCache
    end